request.description:
This endpoint will help you move your candidates through the onboarding flow steps. You have several ways to do this. You can move a candidate to a specific step by making a patch request with the step name. Example:

```
{
    "step": "Phone Interview"
}
```

Or you can move it one step forward or backward relative to its current step. Example:
```
{
    "step": "forward"
}
```
Also, you can move it to the start or end of the flow. Example:
```
{
    "step": "start"
}
```
And finally, you can change it to `approved`, `rejected`, and `withdraw`.
```
{
    "status": "approved"
}
```
